OL,3,CVictims of the Kingsmill atrocity
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,FA commemoration has been held in
OL,7,FKingsmill to mark the 50th anniversary
OL,8,Fof the murders of ten Protestant
OL,9,Fworkmen by IRA gunmen.
OL,11,FThe shooting happened within 24 hours
OL,12,Fof Loyalist paramilitaries targeting
OL,13,Fsix Catholics in their homes just
OL,14,Fmiles away in what was one of the
OL,15,Fworst killing sprees of the Troubles.
OL,17,FOn Monday, relatives returned to the
OL,18,Fsite of the atrocity to lay wreaths.
OL,20,FMay Quinn's brother, Robert Walker,
OL,21,Fwas killed at Kingsmill.
