OL,6,FA 12th man, a Catholic, was saved on
OL,7,Fthe word of his Protestant friends and
OL,8,Fordered to leave the scene before the
OL,9,Fshooting started
OL,11,FThe night before, six Catholics had
OL,12,Fbeen shot - three members of the
OL,13,FO'Dowd family and three Reavey
OL,14,Fbrothers - in a coordinated attack on
OL,15,Ftheir homes by the infamous Loyalist
OL,16,FGlenanne Gang.
