OL,6,FAlan Black, the sole survivor of the
OL,7,FKingsmill massacre, was shot 18 times.
OL,9,F"This is a remembrance of the boys and
OL,10,Fthis is how I want to remember them,
OL,11,Fby a religious dignified service ", he
OL,12,Ftold UTV.
OL,14,FShirley Norris, daughter of Joseph
